Document: nsclient
Title: NSClient++ Manual
Author: NSClient++ Authors
Abstract: Manual for NSClient++ (the nsclient package), a monitoring agent for
 Nagios, Naemon, Icinga and compatible systems. Covers configuration, checks,
 the supported protocols and every module, including those not built in the
 agent-only nsclient package.
Section: System/Monitoring

Format: HTML
Index: /usr/share/doc/nsclient-doc/html/index.html
Files: /usr/share/doc/nsclient-doc/html/*.html
